00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:40,790
Moreover,

290
00:12:41,550 --> 00:12:42,640
Shen Zhong knows me.

291
00:12:43,590 --> 00:12:45,000
He'll be a hidden danger.

292
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:46,960
Don't worry.

293
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,400
You're a shield

294
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:50,110
especially for Shen Zhong.

295
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:51,590
You only need to run the business

296
00:12:51,590 --> 00:12:53,030
and give bribes.

297
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:54,280
Matters concerning the secret agents

298
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,400
will be managed by others.

299
00:12:59,670 --> 00:13:00,320
Who?

300
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:05,670
What if someone comes to examine the shop?

301
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:06,790
The smuggling

302
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:09,150
is a deal with the Beiqi's upper class.

303
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:11,030
Once the profit chain spreads out,

304
00:13:11,030 --> 00:13:12,000
many people will benefit.

305
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,400
No matter what happens,

306
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:15,520
they'll handle it for you.

307
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,080
Unbelievable!

308
00:13:23,350 --> 00:13:24,790
It's dangerous and inefficient

309
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:26,030
to risk your life inquiring about information

310
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:27,550
and hide yourself.

311
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,280
It's time to change your mind.

312
00:13:29,550 --> 00:13:31,150
From now on, with money clearing the way,

313
00:13:31,640 --> 00:13:33,470
we can have our enemy protect us.

314
00:13:33,910 --> 00:13:35,550
But Shen Zhong is against this.

315
00:13:35,550 --> 00:13:37,030
Shen Zhong won't be a problem.

316
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:39,230
It's an irresistible trend.

317
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,110
One man alone can't stop it.

318
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:42,200
That makes sense.

319
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,790
Don't smirk.

320
00:13:58,110 --> 00:13:59,000
Have you heard?

321
00:13:59,000 --> 00:13:59,880
Someone from Nanqing

322
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:01,400
wants to cooperate with us.

323
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:03,280
By the time the trade route opens,

324
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:05,470
it will bring a large sum of money.

325
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:06,320
I heard that

326
00:14:06,350 --> 00:14:07,840
it will be handled by the Embroidered Uniform Guards.

327
00:14:07,910 --> 00:14:09,080
If it succeeds,

328
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,280
our Division will benefit.

329
00:14:10,590 --> 00:14:11,640
I'm afraid it won't be easy.

330
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:12,550
A couple of days ago,

331
00:14:12,590 --> 00:14:14,470
Commander Shen said on the Hall that

332
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:15,910
he wouldn't help to make it happen.

333
00:14:16,470 --> 00:14:17,550
Really?

334
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,710
Haven't you heard about their talks on the Hall?

335
00:14:19,710 --> 00:14:20,350
Tell us about it.

336
00:14:21,110 --> 00:14:22,710
A couple of days ago, Commander Shen said

337
00:14:22,710 --> 00:14:24,110
in front of Her Majesty that...

338
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:32,320
Your Excellency,

339
00:14:32,470 --> 00:14:33,280
your words with Fan Xian

340
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,880
in front of Her Majesty

341
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:36,910
are spreading everywhere.

342
00:14:37,710 --> 00:14:39,280
Fan Xian has made a nice move.

343
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:40,670
However, he forgot that the capital is

344
00:14:41,550 --> 00:14:43,350
controlled by Embroidered Uniform Guards.

345
00:14:49,110 --> 00:14:50,110
Pass on my order to each battalion commanders.

346
00:14:50,470 --> 00:14:51,880
Spare no efforts in blocking the rumor

347
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,030
and check strictly.

348
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:57,400
Are these vegetables picked today?

349
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:57,960
Yes.

350
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,110
They're fresh. Just picked.

351
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:01,840
Have a look!

352
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,030
Fresh pork.

353
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:04,110
Ribs also.

354
00:15:06,590 --> 00:15:08,030
Lady, do you want anything?

355
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,150
It looks good.

356
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:11,200
Just picked.

357
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,150
Give me two.

358
00:15:12,280 --> 00:15:13,670
Shouldn't all Saintesses love

359
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:14,960
ancient calligraphy and paintings

360
00:15:15,110 --> 00:15:16,280
or magic weapons?

361
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:17,760
But I prefer eating.

362
00:15:19,110 --> 00:15:20,000
Please trim them for me.

363
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:20,880
Remove the leaves outside.

364
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:21,710
OK! OK!

365
00:15:21,710 --> 00:15:23,200
The leaves outside are not fresh.

366
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:26,150
Don't put them inside.

367
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:30,640
These are all fresh.

368
00:15:34,590 --> 00:15:35,760
Should you pay attention?

369
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:37,670
To what?

370
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:39,000
You're a Saintess after all.

371
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,590
The basket doesn't go with your temperament.

372
00:15:41,590 --> 00:15:42,760
I'm not in the imperial palace.

373
00:15:43,280 --> 00:15:44,320
You should pay attention to

374
00:15:44,470 --> 00:15:45,520
your temperament all the time.

375
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:46,520
It's not only for pretending

376
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:47,200
in the imperial Palace.

377
00:15:48,230 --> 00:15:49,030
You've got a point.

378
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:52,840
Carry it for me.

379
00:15:58,670 --> 00:15:59,440
I have a question for you.

380
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:00,110
Go ahead.

381
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:02,910
Are you responsible for the rumor

382
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:03,640
in the capital recently?

383
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:04,670
Yes.

384
00:16:06,230 --> 00:16:07,230
Then do you know

385
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,320
Shen Zhong has ordered Embroidered Uniform Guards

386
00:16:09,400 --> 00:16:10,550
to block the information?

387
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:11,550
It won't work.

388
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:15,030
The power of Embroidered Uniform Guards

389
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:16,840
is beyond your imagination.

390
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:19,030
I know, but it still won't work.

391
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,840
How about making a bet?

392
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:23,280
So you're really confident.

393
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:42,280
Your Excellency, do you want to see me?

394
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:44,030
Haven't I given the order?

395
00:16:44,350 --> 00:16:45,320
How come the rumor

396
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,710
is still rampant these days.

397
00:16:48,790 --> 00:16:49,520
Your Excellency,

398
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:51,150
all the battalion commanders said

399
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,400
they had acted according to your order,

400
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,110
but it doesn't work.

401
00:16:54,230 --> 00:16:55,710
I've urged them repeatedly,

402
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:57,150
but they said

403
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,280
they had tried their best.

404
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:00,110
Well...

405
00:17:19,470 --> 00:17:20,680
Why are you so sure

406
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:22,280
the Embroidered Uniform Guards won't take it seriously?

407
00:17:22,830 --> 00:17:24,070
Because they're human.

408
00:17:25,070 --> 00:17:26,070
So what?

409
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:27,880
Humans are selfish.

410
00:17:28,310 --> 00:17:29,920
If the smuggling falls into place,

411
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:31,800
Embroidered Uniform Guards will all benefit

412
00:17:31,800 --> 00:17:32,800
by controlling the financial power.

413
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:33,760
Who doesn't want to

414
00:17:33,950 --> 00:17:35,710
live a better life while alive?

415
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,680
Shen Zhong gets in their way,

416
00:17:38,190 --> 00:17:40,230
so no one wants to help him for sure.

417
00:17:40,710 --> 00:17:41,830
But there must be people who don't seek profits.

418
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,400
Even if they don't seek profits, they will seek power.

419
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:44,710
Shen Zhong controls

420
00:17:44,710 --> 00:17:46,110
Embroidered Uniform Guards all by himself.

421
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,350
If he doesn't step down,

422
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:48,520
how can others move up?

423
00:17:49,350 --> 00:17:50,470
If so,

424
00:17:50,560 --> 00:17:51,350
why didn't they challenge Shen Zhong

425
00:17:51,350 --> 00:17:53,110
as the Commander-in-chief

426
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,110
in earlier years?

427
00:17:54,230 --> 00:17:56,110
In earlier years, he was deeply trusted by the Empress Dowager.

428
00:17:57,310 --> 00:17:58,880
They knew they couldn't beat him,

429
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,160
so they bowed at his feet.

430
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:01,000
What about now?

431
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:03,430
Now with Shangshan Hu rising sharply,

432
00:18:03,430 --> 00:18:04,830
Shen Zhong is no longer the most powerful minister

433
00:18:04,830 --> 00:18:05,710
serving the Empress Dowager.

434
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:06,590
Exactly.

435
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:08,590
Have you planned all of that?

436
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:10,280
Cutting off others' source of income

437
00:18:10,310 --> 00:18:11,400
is similar to killing their parents.

438
00:18:12,590 --> 00:18:13,800
The Embroidered Uniform Guards aren't

439
00:18:13,800 --> 00:18:15,110
the only ones to gain profits from the smuggling.

440
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:16,350
Believe me.

441
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:18,230
If Shen Zhong goes his own way,

442
00:18:19,470 --> 00:18:21,430
he'll become the target of public criticism in the end.

443
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,920
But as long as the Empress Dowager trusts him,

444
00:18:25,280 --> 00:18:26,470
he'll be fine.

445
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:40,520
Keep the birthday celebration simple.

446
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,640
Just share the happiness with the people.

447
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,040
I see.

448
00:18:45,590 --> 00:18:47,110
I'll handle it.

449
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:49,950
You're occupied.

450
00:18:50,280 --> 00:18:51,760
No need to worry about

451
00:18:52,040 --> 00:18:53,560
such a miscellaneous thing.

452
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:56,310
No, that one.

453
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:57,830
But your birthday celebrations have been prepared

454
00:18:57,830 --> 00:18:59,470
by Embroidered Uniform Guards all the time.

455
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:02,800
Yes, indeed.

456
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:05,190
I remember that

457
00:19:05,470 --> 00:19:08,000
your subordinator, the deputy commander,

458
00:19:08,310 --> 00:19:10,230
is quite alert and resourceful.

459
00:19:11,110 --> 00:19:13,710
You can leave this to him.

460
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:14,590
Your Majesty.

461
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:17,160
I'm afraid that you might be too tired.

462
00:19:17,560 --> 00:19:19,430
I have to find someone capable

463
00:19:19,430 --> 00:19:21,430
to assist you.

464
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:25,710
It's my turn. I haven't put down my chess piece.

465
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:28,680
No.

466
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:30,310
That one.

467
00:19:30,590 --> 00:19:32,710
Thank you, Your Majesty.

468
00:19:33,190 --> 00:19:35,040
You may leave.

469
00:19:39,590 --> 00:19:40,640
I win!

470
00:19:44,190 --> 00:19:46,520
Good! Let's play another round.

471
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:56,310
Right, it's different now.

472
00:19:56,430 --> 00:19:57,230
Now the Grand General

473
00:19:57,230 --> 00:19:58,800
is most favored by Her Majesty.

474
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:03,350
Contradicting Her Majesty in face,

475
00:20:03,350 --> 00:20:04,230
no wonder Her Majesty is displeased.

476
00:20:04,230 --> 00:20:05,110
I heard!

477
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:06,800
He's not so trusted as before.

478
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:08,160
Her Majesty seldom summons him.

479
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:28,140
=Shen Mansion=

480
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:35,000
Your Excellency,

481
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:37,110
the tailor has finished

482
00:20:37,110 --> 00:20:38,000
altering your robe.

483
00:20:38,350 --> 00:20:40,000
The python pattern bestowed by

484
00:20:40,230 --> 00:20:41,310
Her Majesty has been embroidered on it.

485
00:21:06,760 --> 00:21:07,560
Your Excellency,

486
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,880
isn't today the day when battalion commanders

487
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,710
from different battalions come to report to you regularly?

488
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:12,560
How come no one

489
00:21:12,560 --> 00:21:13,280
is here?

490
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:16,590
Do I remember the wrong day?

491
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:20,110
Two deputy commanders and two assistant commissioners

492
00:21:20,110 --> 00:21:21,070
have important things to attend to.

493
00:21:21,950 --> 00:21:22,920
Those battalion commanders

494
00:21:23,230 --> 00:21:25,160
are busy working.

495
00:21:26,110 --> 00:21:26,830
They should at least

496
00:21:26,830 --> 00:21:27,920
inform Your Excellency.

497
00:21:31,800 --> 00:21:33,350
It's not bad to be idle.

498
00:21:59,710 --> 00:22:00,520
In your opinion,

499
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:02,110
why does the Empress Dowager

500
00:22:02,110 --> 00:22:03,040
suddenly treat Shen Zhong so coldly?

501
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:05,760
Shen Zhong is too aggressive.

502
00:22:06,310 --> 00:22:07,710
The Empress Dowager didn't mind that before.

503
00:22:08,350 --> 00:22:09,110
It's because he could control

504
00:22:09,230 --> 00:22:10,680
the Embroidered Uniform Guards.

505
00:22:11,040 --> 00:22:12,110
She surely would tolerate

506
00:22:12,190 --> 00:22:13,400
a capable subordinate.

507
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:15,230
But now is different.

508
00:22:15,710 --> 00:22:17,190
The Embroidered Uniform Guards are divided.

509
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:18,760
Your Empress Dowager sees it all.

510
00:22:20,190 --> 00:22:21,950
Actually, she can eliminate

511
00:22:22,230 --> 00:22:23,430
the conspiracies

512
00:22:23,590 --> 00:22:24,950
and recover Shen Zhong's power easily.

513
00:22:25,160 --> 00:22:26,430
Why should she?

514
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:27,800
Ministers getting separated

515
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:28,880
in different cliques

516
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:30,000
by competing for power

517
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:30,830
is better for check and balance.

518
00:22:31,590 --> 00:22:32,880
It's much safer than

519
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:33,640
having only one powerful minister.

520
00:22:34,590 --> 00:22:36,040
But Shen Zhong does everything

521
00:22:36,190 --> 00:22:37,310
out of his loyalty

522
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:38,470
instead of selfness.

523
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:40,070
What does loyalty have to do with that?

524
00:22:40,680 --> 00:22:41,590
In past dynasties,

525
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:43,400
so many loyal ministers were killed.

526
00:22:47,310 --> 00:22:48,230
Where are we heading?

527
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:51,800
I remember you drugged me

528
00:22:52,560 --> 00:22:53,760
when we first met.

529
00:22:54,560 --> 00:22:56,040
Why do you bring that up again?

530
00:22:57,560 --> 00:22:59,160
You lied to me that it was an aphrodisiac.

531
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:01,310
I had no other choice.

532
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:03,190
I thought it's over.

533
00:23:03,190 --> 00:23:04,110
I remember.

534
00:23:05,040 --> 00:23:06,070
Now I'm taking you to

535
00:23:06,070 --> 00:23:07,430
an extremely dangerous place

536
00:23:07,590 --> 00:23:09,160
to avenge the drug.

537
00:23:09,430 --> 00:23:10,310
If you're scared,

538
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:11,430
just don't follow me.

539
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:14,950
To avenge the drug.

540
00:23:16,280 --> 00:23:18,000
You even make a word.

541
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:26,920
Whose home is this?

542
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:28,830
Mine.

543
00:23:36,470 --> 00:23:37,680
Did you grow up here?

544
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:39,760
Not really.

545
00:23:40,800 --> 00:23:42,400
My master asked me to stay in Shangjing.

546
00:23:43,470 --> 00:23:44,590
I love to stay quiet,

547
00:23:45,070 --> 00:23:46,520
so I took this place to grow vegetables.

548
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:47,830
I visit here whenever I'm free.

549
00:23:50,230 --> 00:23:51,280
Are these all grown by you?

550
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:53,520
As to the flowers,

551
00:23:53,560 --> 00:23:54,640
I just scattered the seeds randomly.

552
00:23:54,760 --> 00:23:55,640
I seldom took care of them.

553
00:23:55,710 --> 00:23:56,400
They grow on their own.

554
00:23:59,800 --> 00:24:00,950
She scattered the wild flower seeds

555
00:24:01,190 --> 00:24:03,070
she picked along the road

556
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:05,920
by the wall randomly.

557
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:06,710
She said,

558
00:24:06,710 --> 00:24:07,880
"No need to take care of them.

559
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:10,520
Life can find its way

560
00:24:11,710 --> 00:24:13,880
to thrive."

561
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,040
Who's that "she" you just mentioned?

562
00:24:19,430 --> 00:24:20,350
Your mom said

563
00:24:21,830 --> 00:24:23,230
it has its own destiny.

564
00:24:23,710 --> 00:24:24,470
Let it grow as it likes.

565
00:24:27,350 --> 00:24:27,830
You sound like

566
00:24:27,830 --> 00:24:29,520
a woman I know.

567
00:24:31,560 --> 00:24:32,710
Is she also a Saintess?

568
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:36,640
It's a pity that

569
00:24:37,190 --> 00:24:38,590
the vegetables are not fully grown,

570
00:24:39,070 --> 00:24:40,350
or I wouldn't have to buy vegetables outside.

571
00:24:44,280 --> 00:24:45,000
I'll take it.

572
00:24:47,470 --> 00:24:48,680
So you like farming?

573
00:24:51,190 --> 00:24:53,920
It calms my mind.

574
00:24:56,350 --> 00:24:57,160
Others calm their minds

575
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:58,470
by playing the zither and burning incense.

576
00:24:59,160 --> 00:25:00,160
I like it this way.

577
00:25:07,070 --> 00:25:07,800
